{"tid":1069260,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［原創］廢棄天使","createTime":"2019-03-20T00:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T14:05:43.000Z","uid":216800,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"997b0c63bb6d43f05915da7614ad9abd1669dd90","tid":1069260,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:08:38.000Z","msg":"又係我<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">騎士仔</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次係廢棄天使過程圖<br />\n一開始都無諗住會完成到 搞搞下又得左<br />\n所以好多細節野都無記錄低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去圖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一開始果時<br />\n諗住畫天使x天空</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkS6GKh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkS6GKh.png&h=7ea1a992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫完覺得<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">單調</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">經過一輪構思</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hGLTmKy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhGLTmKy.png&h=6196765c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又變左畫鐵絲網<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">張通告</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYBnZxw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYBnZxw.png&h=fd7bf5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">求其畫個背景落去</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZgbSTC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZgbSTC.png&h=ba7e8509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n差緊少少野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">畫隻我最憎既白鴿落去算</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4T39Eze.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4T39Eze.png&h=e6ef9093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀，又唔錯咁wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">然後上人物個色黎睇下先</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nw8JJ5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNw8JJ5n.png&h=6b1bc587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">搞埋背景</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwoE1O5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwoE1O5.png&h=34f9b383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">搞完</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由於騎士仔好懶 好多地方都唔想執<br />\n所以細微位由佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講開又講<br />\n廢棄天使個主題其實自己都覺得唔錯<br />\n再用香港咁既地方作故事背景 <br />\n畫下人渴望自由既野之類 又幾正咁<br />\n加上自己又鍾意畫背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n手多多畫多張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3mfAa2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3mfAa2.png&h=6f056ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUdJJ4o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUdJJ4o.png&h=c169f447&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf0f540cdce64b17a29d8d180875bd9786bf46c0","tid":1069260,"uid":225916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:11:30.000Z","msg":"巴打勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名"},{"pid":"53abf95a877eabe20e6039062f69fc9dc8b73a7a","tid":1069260,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf0f540cdce64b17a29d8d180875bd9786bf46c0","tid":1069260,"uid":225916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:11:30.000Z","msg":"巴打勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:25:14.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f65a244816bc0617e6916c0ee0c96f82995488a","tid":1069260,"uid":241895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZ5zQTb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZ5zQTb.jpg&h=a7cedecd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n諗到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(no offense)"},{"pid":"289e3426cdcc443aa741b992eb17012b9053a9d0","tid":1069260,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f65a244816bc0617e6916c0ee0c96f82995488a","tid":1069260,"uid":241895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZ5zQTb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZ5zQTb.jpg&h=a7cedecd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n諗到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(no offense)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:00:14.000Z","msg":"竟然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n凌波身材正啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4bc4edb851f331e5bd34cba925709fc2fa66a3","tid":1069260,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:05:39.000Z","msg":"巴打好慘 好野冇人理<br />\n有時真係好無奈 冇人識印賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫你推"},{"pid":"7a70c1557b19181e7fce24b46caf6aeb0109720e","tid":1069260,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c4bc4edb851f331e5bd34cba925709fc2fa66a3","tid":1069260,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:05:39.000Z","msg":"巴打好慘 好野冇人理<br />\n有時真係好無奈 冇人識印賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫你推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:06:06.000Z","msg":"*欣"},{"pid":"dc8e6592948266ce4713ec9d790bd47910fab99b","tid":1069260,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c4bc4edb851f331e5bd34cba925709fc2fa66a3","tid":1069260,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:05:39.000Z","msg":"巴打好慘 好野冇人理<br />\n有時真係好無奈 冇人識印賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫你推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:10:57.000Z","msg":"慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算得一個有睇有留言已滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46101f9f3af65a42793379ce6d7241b2d8840eb2","tid":1069260,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"ecc3c8a1c77ea33f1d02a622650b2c735dede58b","tid":1069260,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"以為又係猿生"},{"pid":"f04f454c55a6ca30bf3c4a6df068b230dfaca2a3","tid":1069260,"uid":178682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"Ok la"},{"pid":"304d558d9080221caffa3479af7001cd1ec6108b","tid":1069260,"uid":216800,"like":